      "source": [
        "* 1. สร้างนิยามของป้ายชื่อ (Label define)\n",
        "label define yesno_lab 0 \"No\" 1 \"Yes\"\n",
        "label define sex_lab 0 \"Female\" 1 \"Male\"\n",
        "\n",
        "* 2. นำป้ายชื่อไปแปะที่ตัวแปร (Label values)\n",
        "label values anaemia diabetes high_blood_pressure smoking death_event yesno_lab\n",
        "label values sex sex_lab\n",
        "\n",
        "* 3. เช็กผลลัพธ์\n",
        "tabulate high_blood_pressure"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "** พรรณา\n",
        "dtable, by(high_blood_pressure, test total) ///\n",
        "    continuous(age creatinine_phosphokinase ejection_fraction platelets serum_creatinine serum_sodium time, statistics(p50 p25 p75) test(kwallis)) ///\n",
        "    factor(anaemia diabetes smoking death_event sex, statistics(fvfreq fvpercent) test(pearson)) ///\n",
        "    nformat(%9.2f p50 p25 p75 fvpercent)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "**การจับคู่ด้วยคะแนนความน่าจะเป็น (PSM Execution)\n",
        "**รัน psmatch2 เพื่อจับคู่กลุ่ม (Control vs Treatment)\n",
        "* (ใช้ high_blood_pressure เป็น Treatment และ DEATH_EVENT เป็น Outcome)\n",
        "psmatch2 high_blood_pressure age anaemia creatinine_phosphokinase diabetes ejection_fraction platelets serum_creatinine serum_sodium sex smoking, outcome(death_event) logit\n",
        "\n",
        "**การตรวจสอบความสมดุลของการจับคู่ (Balance Check)\n",
        "pstest age anaemia creatinine_phosphokinase diabetes ejection_fraction platelets serum_creatinine serum_sodium sex smoking, both graph\n",
        "\n",
        "* สั่งทำกราฟจุดเพื่อดูความต่าง (Standardized Mean Difference)\n",
        "pstest age anaemia creatinine_phosphokinase diabetes ejection_fraction platelets serum_creatinine serum_sodium sex smoking, graph\n",
        "\n",
        "**การแสดงผลกราฟิก (Visualization)\n",
        "psgraph"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "* เพิ่มออปชัน caliper(0.05) และ common\n",
        "psmatch2 high_blood_pressure age anaemia creatinine_phosphokinase diabetes ejection_fraction platelets serum_creatinine serum_sodium sex smoking, outcome(death_event) logit \n",
        "\n",
        "* วาดกราฟภูเขา (Density Plot) แยก 2 กลุ่ม\n",
        "twoway (kdensity _pscore if high_blood_pressure==1, color(red%50) recast(area)) ///\n",
        "       (kdensity _pscore if high_blood_pressure==0, color(blue%50) recast(area)), ///\n",
        "       legend(order(1 \"High BP (Treatment)\" 2 \"Normal (Control)\")) ///\n",
        "       xtitle(\"Propensity Score\") ytitle(\"Density\") ///\n",
        "       title(\"Propensity Score Distribution (Mountain Plot)\")"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
